  "keyFeatures": [
    "JIT compilation via LLVM backend and custom YVM bytecode backend",
    "Borrow checker for memory safety without garbage collection overhead",
    "Optional garbage-collected references (gcnew / ^T) for shared ownership",
    "Statically typed with type inference and generic type parameters",
    "Operator overloading and interface (trait) system",
    "Coroutine-based fiber runtime for lightweight async execution",
    "Embeddable C++20 library with a clean host API for calling C++ functions from Yoyo and vice versa",
    "String interpolation (${expr} syntax)",
    "Sum types (unions), product types (structs/classes), optional and result types",
    "Macro system for compile-time code generation"
  ],
